#: temp.glade:2391
msgid "PTXprint: Generate Front Matter"
msgstr "PTXprint : Générer les pages liminaires"

#: temp.glade:2476
msgid "BASIC: Front matter contains just a few\n"
"essentials with publication information"
msgstr "BASIQUE : Les pages liminaires ne contient que quelques\n"
"éléments essentiels avec les informations de publication"

#: temp.glade:2478
msgid "Generate front matter: BASIC (just the essentials)"
msgstr "Générer la page de garde : BASIQUE (juste l'essentiel)"

#: temp.glade:2482
msgid "This option will create a simple verso page\n"
"containing essential copyright and licensing\n"
"information followed by a table of contents."
msgstr "Cette option créera une simple page verso contenant\n"
"des informations essentielles sur le droit d'auteur et\n"
"la licence suivies d'une table des matières."

#: temp.glade:2500
msgid "ADVANCED: template contains several sections\n"
"(some of which require editing before use)"
msgstr "AVANCÉ : le modèle contient plusieurs sections\n"
"(dont certaines nécessitent une modification avant d'utilisation)"

#: temp.glade:2502
msgid "Generate front matter: ADVANCED (requires editing)"
msgstr "Générer la page de garde : AVANCÉ (nécessite une édition)"

#: temp.glade:2506
msgid "This option will create an extensive template\n"
"with multiple sections (each of which will start\n"
"on a new page in the final publication). You will\n"
"need to edit the sample text provided so that it\n"
"communicates in the required language(s).\n"
"You can also remove unwanted sections if they\n"
"are inappropriate for this publication.\n"
"Note: In order to make this template generic for\n"
"several different publications in this project, you\n"
"are encouraged to use \\zvar|variables\\*  which will be\n"
"replaced with publication-specific info when printed.\n"
"For example:\n"
"\\mt1 \\zvar|maintitle\\*\n"
"\\mt2 \\zvar|subtitle\\*\n"
"\\pc \\zvar|maintitlefr\\*\n"
"\\pc \\zvar|subtitlefr\\*\n"
"\\pc \\zvar|languagename\\*\n"
"\\pc \\zvar|copiesprinted\\*"
msgstr "Cette option créera un modèle étendu avec plusieurs sections\n"
"(dont chacune commencera sur une nouvelle page dans la\n"
"publication finale). Vous devrez modifier l'exemple de texte\n"
"fourni afin qu'il communique dans la ou les langue(s) requise(s).\n"
"Vous pouvez également supprimer les sections indésirables si elles\n"
"sont inappropriées pour cette publication.\n"
"Note : Afin de rendre ce modèle générique pour plusieurs\n"
"publications différentes dans ce projet, vous êtes encouragé\n"
"à utiliser des \\zvar|variables\\* qui seront remplacées par des\n"
"infos spécifiques à la publication lors de l'impression.\n"
"Par exemple :\n"
"\\mt1 \\zvar|maintitle\\*\n"
"\\mt2 \\zvar|subtitle\\*\n"
"\\pc \\zvar|maintitlefr\\*.\n"
"\\pc \\zvar|subtitlefr\\*\n"
"\\pc \\zvar|languagename\\*\n"
"\\pc \\zvar|copiesprinted\\*"

#: temp.glade:2538
msgid "Include sections for a separate cover page"
msgstr "Inclure les sections pour une page de couverture séparée"

#: temp.glade:2539
msgid "Generate front matter: Include sections for cover page"
msgstr "Générer la page de garde : Inclure les sections pour la page de couverture"

#: temp.glade:2543
msgid "(Not yet implemented)\n"
"Enable this option if you want to include the following\n"
"sections (used for creating a cover page):\n"
"\\periph Cover - detailing text and optional picture\n"
"\\periph Spine - text for the spine of the cover"
msgstr "(Pas encore implémenté)\n"
"Activez cette option si vous souhaitez inclure les sections\n"
"suivantes (utilisées pour créer une page de couverture) :\n"
"\\periph Couverture - texte de détail et image facultative\n"
"\\periph Dos - texte pour le dos de la couverture"

#: temp.glade:2579 temp.glade:2952
msgid "Warning!"
msgstr "Attention !"

#: temp.glade:2594
msgid "This operation can overwrite\n"
"carefully crafted settings.\n"
"So choose carefully...\n"
"If in doubt, click Cancel."
msgstr ""

#: temp.glade:2609
msgid "DIGLOT: template for a Diglot or Polyglot publication\n"
"(deliberately fuller — delete sections you do not need)"
msgstr ""

#: temp.glade:2611
msgid "Generate front matter: DIGLOT (for Diglot/Polyglot publications)"
msgstr ""

#: temp.glade:2615
msgid "This option creates a DIGLOT / POLYGLOT front matter\n"
"template designed for publications with two (or more)\n"
"languages or scripts. It is deliberately more complete\n"
"than the BASIC and ADVANCED templates because diglots\n"
"are inherently complex: two (or more) texts, often two\n"
"contents lists, two prefaces, sometimes two scripts and\n"
"two writing directions. Delete the sections you do not need.\n\n"
"Like the ADVANCED template it uses \\zvar|variables\\* and\n"
"\\zglot|L\\* / \\zglot|R\\* markers for column-specific content,\n"
"so it requires editing before use and is NOT suitable for\n"
"use inside Paratext without prior modification.\n\n"
"If this option is disabled, the Diglot setting is not\n"
"enabled for this configuration."
msgstr ""

#: temp.glade:2644
msgid "PARATEXT: Make a copy of the Project's FRT book\n"
"(which may be edited to make use of \\zvar|variables\\*)"
msgstr ""

#: temp.glade:2646
msgid "Generate front matter: PARATEXT (make a local copy)"
msgstr "Générer la page de garde : PARATEXT (faire une copie locale)"

#: temp.glade:2650
msgid "This option will create a COPY of the Paratext project's\n"
"FRT book to be used exclusively by PTXprint. You can\n"
"edit the front matter to make use of PTXprint-specific\n"
"\\zvar|variables\\* but note that none of these edits will\n"
"be reflected in Paratext. In addition, if you edit the FRT\n"
"book in Paratext, those changes will not be reflected\n"
"here until you regenerate this (local) Front Matter.\n\n"
"If option is disabled, it is due to not having a FRT book\n"
"in the Paratext project (so there is nothing to import)."
msgstr ""

#: temp.glade:2701
msgid "Generate Front Matter"
msgstr "Générer les pages liminaires"

