"default Colophon text markers which\n"
"include the Copyright statement tag,\n"
"the License statement tag, and the\n"
"Illustration credits tag."
msgstr "Cliquer sur ce bouton rechargera les marqueurs de texte \n"
"par défaut Colophon qui\n"
"incluent la balise Copyright statement tag,\n"
"la balise License state, et la balise\n"
"Illustration credits."

